title: Marc Jacobs' nude selfie blunder
text:
Marc Jacobs' nude selfie blunder 
Thursday 2 Jul 2015 6:33 a.m. 
Marc Jacobs (AAP) 
Fashion designer Marc Jacobs suffered an embarrassing social media blunder on Tuesday when he posted a nude 'selfie' to his public Instagram page. 
The picture shows the US style guru with his underwear pulled down his legs, taking a picture of his exposed butt in the mirror of his closet, and his penis can also be seen. 
In the caption, Jacobs writes, "It's yours to try!" and it is thought he accidentally made the picture public instead of sending it in a private direct message to a specific friend. 
The saucy snap was quickly removed, but not before an eagle-eyed fan took a copy of the image. Jacobs had not commented on the incident as WENN went to press. 
WENN.com
